cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "Buildings.Shanghai"
abstract: >
  End-to-end UBEM pipeline for Shanghai: data acquisition, ML archetype
  inference, EnergyPlus simulation, embodied carbon Monte Carlo, calibration
  and figures. Extends the Buildings.city framework (Lyu et al., 2026) to a
  Chinese hot-summer / cold-winter megacity.
